about.summary: Earth Engine <https://earthengine.google.com/> client library for R. All of the 'Earth Engine' API classes, modules, and functions are made available. Additional functions implemented include importing (exporting) of Earth Engine spatial objects, extraction of time series, interactive map display, assets management interface, and metadata display. See <https://r-spatial.github.io/rgee/> for further details.

name: r-rgee
raw_recipe:
{% set version = '1.1.0' %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rgee
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/rgee_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/rgee/rgee_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d9a7944531f308c166a9c816627138fdaeb3a8da5ebfc64d3a0fb5a0f058f519

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-r6
    - r-cli
    - r-crayon
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-leafem
    - r-leaflet >=2.0.2
    - r-magrittr
    - r-processx
    - r-reticulate >=1.15

  run:
    - r-base
    - r-r6
    - r-cli
    - r-crayon
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-leafem
    - r-leaflet >=2.0.2
    - r-magrittr
    - r-processx
    - r-reticulate >=1.15

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('rgee')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('rgee')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/r-spatial/rgee/, https://r-spatial.github.io/rgee/, https://github.com/google/earthengine-api/

  license: Apache-2.0
  summary: Earth Engine <https://earthengine.google.com/> client library for R. All of the 'Earth
    Engine' API classes, modules, and functions are made available. Additional functions
    implemented include importing (exporting) of Earth Engine spatial objects, extraction
    of time series, interactive map display, assets management interface, and metadata
    display. See <https://r-spatial.github.io/rgee/> for further details.

  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE.md

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - csaybar
    - davemlz
